WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.133 --> 00:00:01.700
Luoxue Love's design

2
00:00:01.700 --> 00:00:03.400
I drew it a few months ago

3
00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:05.266
And I have this design right now.

4
00:00:05.266 --> 00:00:07.400
I optimized it on the previous version

5
00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:08.700
Isn't it obvious enough?

6
00:00:08.900 --> 00:00:09.966
You are talking nonsense.

7
00:00:09.966 --> 00:00:12.133
This blueprint is clearly drawn by me

8
00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:14.100
Obviously, you are the one who draws the tiger but not the anti-dog.

9
00:00:14.100 --> 00:00:15.800
So it's different?

10
00:00:21.866 --> 00:00:23.566
Mom, you're awake

11
00:00:25.133 --> 00:00:26.033
Miss you

12
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:28.066
Where did it go?

13
00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:31.400
Mom already knows her situation

14
00:00:31.600 --> 00:00:32.700
Are we dead?

15
00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:34.100
Mom, don't worry.

16
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:35.900
I have a way

17
00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:38.400
Yes mom

18
00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:40.766
It's the blueprint I lost earlier.

19
00:00:40.766 --> 00:00:42.600
Belozzione was robbed

20
00:00:42.766 --> 00:00:44.200
Please help me prove it

21
00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:46.000
I drew this blueprint

22
00:00:48.966 --> 00:00:52.400
Lin Hong, you have been working in our family for 15 years

23
00:00:52.400 --> 00:00:54.666
I want you to be honest.

24
00:00:55.566 --> 00:00:57.366
Xueqin is stronger by nature

25
00:00:57.366 --> 00:00:58.933
If I tell the truth

26
00:00:58.933 --> 00:01:01.566
I'm afraid he can't do it wrong.

27
00:01:01.566 --> 00:01:05.500
But if I lie and say that the blueprints are mine, Xueqin

28
00:01:05.733 --> 00:01:07.766
How can you live up to your nostalgia?

29
00:01:09.966 --> 00:01:11.066
Aunt Soul

30
00:01:11.133 --> 00:01:13.666
This blueprint is very important to me

31
00:01:13.700 --> 00:01:16.766
You have to think about it, Mom.

32
00:01:19.466 --> 00:01:21.400
I kiss a word

